# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok eight people were nabbed by police friday as suspects in a crime ring that reportedly extorted at least nt$ # million from olympic gold medalist chu <unk> by setting up a sex trap on the internet , according to police .
# ::alignments
(n / nab-01
      :ARG0 (p / police)
      :ARG1 (p2 / person
            :quant 8
            :ARG2-of (s / suspect-01
                  :ARG1 (r / ring
                        :mod (c / crime-02)
                        :ARG0-of (e / extort-01
                              :ARG1 (a / at-least
                                    :op1 (m / monetary-quantity
                                          :quant 1000000
                                          :unit (d / dollar)))
                              :ARG2 (p3 / person
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Chu")
                                    :ARG0-of (m2 / medal-01
                                          :ARG1 (g / gold)
                                          :mod (g2 / game
                                                :name (n3 / name
                                                      :op1 "Olympics"))))
                              :ARG1-of (r2 / report-01)
                              :manner (s2 / set-up-03
                                    :ARG0 p3
                                    :ARG1 (t / trap-01
                                          :mod (s3 / sex-01))
                                    :location (ii / internet))))))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday)))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok thai foreign minister surakiart sathirathai responded angrily to us senate criticism that thailand had been acting as a `` mouthpiece '' for myanmar 's ruling government , the nation newspaper reported saturday .

                                    :op1 "Thailand"))
                        :ARG2 (m / minister
                              :topic (f / foreign))))
            :ARG1 (c2 / criticize-01
                  :ARG0 (g / government-organization
                        :name (n5 / name
                              :op1 "Senate"))
                  :ARG1 c
                  :ARG2 (a / act-01
                        :ARG0 c
                        :ARG1 (m2 / mouthpiece)
                        :beneficiary (g2 / government-organization
                              :ARG0-of (g3 / govern-01
                                    :ARG1 (c3 / country
                                          :name (n6 / name
                                                :op1 "Myanmar")))
                              :ARG0-of (r3 / rule-03))))
            :manner (a2 / angry))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (s / saturday)))

                        :unit (d / day))))

            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (f / fly-01
                  :mod (c2 / cargo)
                  :ARG1-of (s2 / schedule-01
                        :ARG1-of (r2 / regular-02))
                  :source (c3 / city
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Beijing"))
                  :destination (c4 / city
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Ulan"
                              :op2 "Bator")
                        :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (p / province
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "Mongolia"))
                              :ARG2 (c5 / capital))))
            :ARG1-of (b2 / begin-01
                  :time (d2 / date-entity
                        :month 2))))

            :weekday (f3 / friday)))

# ::alignments
(t / text
      :part-of (r / resolution
            :ARG1-of (ii / issue-01
                  :ARG0 (c / cabinet
                        :poss (p / person
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Fayez"
                                    :op2 "Tarawneh")
                              :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG2 (m / minister
                                          :mod (p2 / prime))))
                        :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (c2 / country
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Jordan"))
                              :ARG2 (m2 / member))))
            :ARG0-of (d / declare-02
                  :ARG1 (h3 / hussein
                        :poss (p3 / person
                              :ARG0-of (h4 / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG1 c2
                                    :ARG2 (k / king)))
                        :ARG2 (f / fit-03
                              :polarity -
                              :ARG1 h3
                              :ARG2 (r2 / rule-03
                                    :ARG0 h3)))
                  :ARG0-of (t2 / transfer-01
                        :ARG1 (a / authority
                              :mod (a2 / all))
                        :ARG2 (p4 / person
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Abdullah")
                              :ARG0-of (h5 / have-rel-role-91
                                    :ARG1 p3
                                    :ARG2 (a3 / and
                                          :op1 (s / son
                                                :ARG1-of (h6 / have-degree-91
                                                      :ARG2 (o / old)
                                                      :ARG3 (m3 / most)))
                                          :op2 (h7 / heir
                                                :mod (c3 / crown))
                                          :age (t3 / temporal-quantity
                                                :quant 1
                                                :unit (y / year)))))))))

# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (s2 / source
            :mod (m / medicine))
      :ARG1 (l / launch-01
            :ARG0 (w / warplane
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "United"
                              :op2 "States")))
            :ARG1 (s3 / strike-01
                  :ARG0 w
                  :ARG1 (p / position
                        :location-of (ii / insurgent))
                  :location (c2 / city
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Hit")
                        :location (w2 / west
                              :part-of c
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Iraq"))))
            :mod (a / air))
      :ARG0-of (c3 / cause-01
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (k / kill-01
                        :ARG0 w
                        :ARG1 (p2 / person
                              :quant 6
                              :mod c))
                  :op2 (w3 / wound-01
                        :ARG0 w
                        :ARG1 (p3 / person
                              :mod (o / other)))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday)))

                        :name (n2 / name

                  :op1 (n3 / now)

                        :op1 (t / temporal-quantity
                              :quant 1
                              :unit (d / day)))))
      :time (t2 / today))

      :ARG0 (d / department
            :topic (f / foreign))
      :ARG1 (o / offer-01
            :ARG0 (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "United"
                        :op2 "States"))
            :ARG1 (ii / incentivize-01
                  :ARG0 c
                  :ARG1 (p / person
                        :ARG0-of (s2 / seek-01
                              :ARG1 (a / asylum))
                        :mod (c2 / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Vietnam")))
                  :ARG2 (r / return-01
                        :ARG1 p
                        :ARG4 (h / home)
                        :time (a2 / after
                              :op1 (r2 / reject-01
                                    :ARG0 (c3 / city
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "Washington"))
                                    :ARG1 (a3 / apply-01
                                          :ARG0 p
                                          :ARG1 (r3 / resettle-01
                                                :ARG1 p)))))
                  :mod (c4 / cash))
            :ARG3 p
            :location (h2 / here))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (s3 / sunday)))

# ::alignments
(c / comedy
      :ARG0-of (r / romantic-03)
      :ARG1-of (a / affable-02
            :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                  :ARG2 (a2 / affable-02
                        :ARG1 c)
                  :ARG3 (m / more
                        :mod (e / even))))
      :ARG1-of (h2 / have-degree-91
            :ARG2 r)
      :ARG3 (m2 / more)
      :condition (ii / intend-01
            :polarity -
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (a3 / assert-02
                  :ARG0 c
                  :ARG1 (c2 / cuteness
                        :poss c))
            :degree (s / so))
      :domain (ii2 / it))
